{
  "texts": [
    "Proofreading annotations for each location along with the CPC maps and random seeds used during sampling are included with this submission.",
    "Serial section EM images of a cubic millimeter volume of mouse cortex were acquired at the Allen Institute 4, 5.",
    "The images were aligned using a preliminary version of our pipeline.",
    "The connectomics team at the Allen Institute for Brain Sciences stitched and aligned the image stack to displacements within 20 μm using their ASAP framework 35, 36.",
    "The coarse alignment was further refined using an Encoder trained to optimize patch matching correlograms for 1024 nm data as described in Buniatyan, et al., 2020."
  ]
}